25|$|The Fisher House {{program is}} a private-public {{partnership}} that supports America's military in their time of need. The program recognizes the special sacrifices {{of the men and}} <b>women</b> <b>in</b> <b>uniform</b> and the hardships of military service by meeting a humanitarian need beyond what is normally provided by the U.S. Department of Defense and U.S. Department of Veterans Affairs.|$|E
